div.div: SSS-geup Teukseongeul Badatjiman Jeokdanghi Salgo Sipda

The world now swarms with supernatural beings called Celestials and the Awakened, people with newfound special powers. But none of this means anything to Yoo Sungwon, an ordinary man trying to live an ordinary life. Unfortunately for him, his peaceful days end when he gets a mysterious text and becomes a rare SSS-class knight with perks to die for. In order to avoid getting killed or targeted by those who want his powers for their own, Sungwon has no choice but to get stronger by leveling up.
(Source: Tapas)

Earth in the 21st century has fused with another world. An era of dungeons teeming with monsters, the adventurers that raid them, and the most elite educational facility in South Korea that fosters these adventurers: Warrior High School.
Although he was once considered the greatest adventurers in Asia, he has been accused with false chargers and, while dungeon smuggling in order to pay for his sick fathers medical treatments, Yoo Jaryong comes across a teen.
You there, get in Warrior High School.
This is a story about a young man whos lost his dream and hiding his identity finding himself once again.
